President: [+ president +] ([?if president_party = "I":<span style="color: #808080;">**I**</span>?][?if president_party = "SPD":<span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span>?][?if president_party = "Z":<span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span>?][?if president_party = nlp_name:<span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span>?][?if president_party = "DNVP":<span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span>?])

Chancellor: [+ chancellor +] ([?if chancellor_party = "SPD":<span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span>?][?if chancellor_party = "Z":<span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span>?][?if chancellor_party = nlp_name:<span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span>?])

Vice-Chancellor: [+ vice_chancellor +] ([?if vice_chancellor_party = "Z":<span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span>?][?if vice_chancellor_party = nlp_name:<span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span>?][?if vice_chancellor_party = "KVP":<span style="color: #455B95;">**KVP**</span>?][?if vice_chancellor_party = "DNVP":<span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span>?])

